3731456fde4","tid":36549,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>袁澧林係超聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢提名最二多，唔擺去超想我擺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e0fa9413898af545089d5086b74bbea0670dac","tid":36549,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會太複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec83b1f167915003eb8e4bc7b3798e1645c82b58","tid":36549,"uid":43619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37aca80678a0e1e5799dc4583283bd3d15de94df","tid":36549,"uid":33861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"其實巴打真係好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係將個賽制拉到咁長我覺得過唔到67輪<br />\nd人就會開始又嫌煩又盛<br />\n投票數字會大減<br />\n之後就會有人出黎話都有冇人投不如執柒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得巴打不如慢慢黎<br />\n整好左超聯同冠聯先<br />\n反應好先再整埋甲同乙組<br />\n廢時浪費巴打你一番心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cf9cb3331a705be22d82ee953da091e9568e67","tid":36549,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實巴打真係好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係將個賽制拉到咁長我覺得過唔到67輪<br />\nd人就會開始又嫌煩又盛<br />\n投票數字會大減<br />\n之後就會有人出黎話都有冇人投不如執柒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得巴打不如慢慢黎<br />\n整好左超聯同冠聯先<br />\n反應好先再整埋甲同乙組<br />\n廢時浪費巴打你一番心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7a2a0e41ea9b654a5655d76d7937d2d2b2cb39","tid":36549,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實巴打真係好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係將個賽制拉到咁長我覺得過唔到67輪<br />\nd人就會開始又嫌煩又盛<br />\n投票數字會大減<br />\n之後就會有人出黎話都有冇人投不如執柒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得巴打不如慢慢黎<br />\n整好左超聯同冠聯先<br />\n反應好先再整埋甲同乙組<br />\n廢時浪費巴打你一番心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打你既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無人投都可以係一種表態黎，球賽入座率都唔會場場爆啦，其實拖長黎搞，係一個機會比大家隨時可以玩，唔得閒既話唔投都無問題，反正舊制選舉只係一年搞一次，一個月貨仔，其餘時間空晒，但今次就係比個渠道大家比以前再多啲時間參與其中樂在其中<br />\n同埋每輪group埋一齊玩,我諗lihkg既巴打都唔會喺每日幾千定過萬個新post裏面容納唔到區區一個投票post掛<br />\n至於如果咁樣都有人話執柒，我尊重但唔會認同<br />\n始終甲乙兩組既女係好多巴打投完玩過附加賽先得出黎，如果我忽然又cut左佢，呢種朝令夕改既做法只會令其他巴打對賽事失去信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0ae5cf017a2a8c366ada26c0f56f8d7d6dd015","tid":36549,"uid":34999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:23:00.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e516f5fef3ef8b686ccbe9fc1bc07de19169345e","tid":36549,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"會唔會打季後賽？ ?.?"},{"pid":"dfcb159b07fbd47fae53095626721f56587ef1af","tid":36549,"uid":31677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"如果定期比賽都可以養個投票習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a73b7c574ea8a27b6f57cf93f37c75561307ee1","tid":36549,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會打季後賽？ ?.?</blockquote><br />\nnba咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過諗緊會唔會有一個四個組別冠軍既四角友賽，同埋有巴打之前反映過想有外國好手，休季果時可以諗諗由巴打們推介各國女神，搞個海外邀請賽，但暫時只係空想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞好依家呢個賽季先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5114cc278c30a96a4edfa9552787f774403920","tid":36549,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果定期比賽都可以養個投票習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我正係呢個意思<br />\n如果平時連上網撳制投票都懶，真係唔敢想像<br />\n同埋投票既好習慣往往由娛樂既活動開始，就好似日本都有啲組合會搞投票果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0fbf745ebe7b097258bf5efd76428b795d0485","tid":36549,"uid":13400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"無我？"},{"pid":"091174ea199c8204ea832475e74879e0d018c0a5","tid":36549,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無我？</blockquote><br />\n無人提名你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b312204aa05e61bdc55d97d47133582e48ee4a9","tid":36549,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}